prompts.prompt: Create a calculator component that can take 2 number as input and has ability to do the basic math operations and show the results. Show the numbers 0-9 as small buttons along with the operations. Make the component very well styled and beautiful,  add to the home page

Create a Django e-commerce project for a textile company that sells its products to different schools. The project should include different login pages and logo management for each school's users. It should also allow for the management of single and combined products.
